title: MTSU snaps skid with win over FIU
text:
MTSU snaps skid with win over FIU 
Updated: Sat, Oct 17 2015, 10:48 PM 
Stream WZTV Fox 17 Newscasts LIVE starting with Fox 17 This Morning at 4:30am, News at 5:30pm and News at 9pm & 10 pm 
Middle Tennessee snaps a 3-game losing streak with a 42-34 victory over FIU. Fox 17's Dan Phillips has highlights of the Blue Raiders victory!
